name: Super Simple Survey Creator
description:
This document has been designed to help you quickly generate offline materials in which to gather feedback, survey your audience, or just generally inform your approach based on user insight.


All components have been built using auto layout, so all you have to do is drag and drop elements onto a page and add any additional styling you wish.


This is the very first iteration of a document I hope to expand on. If you have any suggestions or feedback please send it to me at


ryantinsley.design/contact
